Breast_Composition: fibro fatty and glandular breast parenchyma (ACR B).
Findings:
multiple well-defined soft opacities with popcorn calcifications seen in the central inner and outer quadrant of

skin and nipple appear normal.  

few coarse and round calcifications seen in the outer quadrant.
